Properties.Caption: Просмотр событий КО
Properties.Tag: Select [K_BD].[CBD] As [Код бюджета], [DOC_DO].[CDO] As [№ кредитного договора], Max([DOC_1].[DDOC]) As [Дата кредитного договора], Max([DOC_DO].[COMMENT]) As [Наименование договора], [DCO].[UCDOC] As [№ обязательства], Max([DOC_DO_1].[COMMENT]) As [Наименование обязательства], [DOC_1].[CDOC] As [Документ], [K_VAL].[CVAL] As [Валюта], Max([K_VAL].[NVAL]) As [Наименование валюты], [DCO_EV_L].[DCO_EV_LID] As [Идентификатор события КО], Month([DCO_EV_L].[D_EV]) As [Месяц даты события], Day([DCO_EV_L].[D_EV]) As [День даты события], Year([DCO_EV_L].[D_EV]) As [Год даты события] From ((((((((((((([DCO] With (NoLock) Inner Join [K_FDO] With (NoLock) On ([DCO].[K_FDOID]=[K_FDO].[K_FDOID])) Inner Join [DCO_EV_L] With (NoLock) On ([DCO].[DCOID]=[DCO_EV_L].[DCOID])) Inner Join [K_CHDCO] With (NoLock) On ([DCO_EV_L].[K_CHDCOID]=[K_CHDCO].[K_CHDCOID])) Inner Join [K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([DCO_EV_L].[K_ULID]=[K_UL].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] As [K_UL_KF] With (NoLock) On ([DCO_EV_L].[K_ULID_KF]=[K_UL_KF].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_VAL] With (NoLock) On ([DCO].[K_VALID]=[K_VAL].[K_VALID])) Inner Join [DOC] With (NoLock) On ([DCO].[DOCID]=[DOC].[DOCID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[Apps_GroupsID]=[Apps_Groups].[Apps_GroupsID])) Inner Join [K_BD] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_BDID]=[K_BD].[K_BDID])) Left Join [DOC_DO] As [DOC_DO_1] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[DOCID]=[DOC_DO_1].[DOCID])) Inner Join [DOC_DOC] With (NoLock) On ([DCO].[DOCID]=[DOC_DOC].[DOCID])) Inner Join [DOC] As [DOC_1] With (NoLock) On ([DOC_DOC].[DOCID_PARENT]=[DOC_1].[DOCID] And [DOC_DOC].[K_TDID_PARENT]=[DOC_1].[K_TDID])) Left Join [DOC_DO] With (NoLock) On ([DOC_1].[DOCID]=[DOC_DO].[DOCID])) Where |0 Group by [K_BD].[CBD], [DOC_DO].[CDO], [DOC_1].[CDOC], [DCO].[UCDOC], [K_VAL].[CVAL], [DCO_EV_L].[DCO_EV_LID], Month([DCO_EV_L].[D_EV]), Day([DCO_EV_L].[D_EV]), Year([DCO_EV_L].[D_EV]) Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр событий КО
